Setting up VS Code Installing Node and NPM
npm init react-app firstapp
cd firstapp
npm start
In order to run and view your React app, open VS Code built-in terminal, run npm start, and then click Open Development server (on the blue horizontal bar at the bottom) or right click on the file and Open Preview
